p.k: Gumball and Darwin try to get a game back from Tobias, but Darwin starts to feel like a sidekick to Gumball and refuses to follow his orders. / Vice Principal Brown gives Gumball and Darwin the ancient school hamster, Chris Morris, to look after for the weekend. / Gumball and Darwin argue with the Internet. / Gumball and Darwin try to find out the name of their neighbour, Antlers Guy, but accidentally blow his witness protection cover.
